    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped as not-assessed per MRL 2 guidelines. The CFD model demonstrates adequate predictive capability for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied across all operating points. The assessment team accepts the model for the stated COU.",
